# Comprehensive Markdown Guide
## Introduction to Advanced Markdown Features

### 1. Text Formatting Basics

This is *italic* and this is **bold**
Here's ***bold italic*** text
~~Strikethrough~~ text
`inline code`

### 2. Lists

#### Ordered List
1. First item
2. Second item
   1. Sub-item 2.1
   2. Sub-item 2.2
3. Third item

#### Unordered List
* Item one
  * Sub-item
  * Sub-item
* Item two
* Item three

### 3. Blockquotes

> This is a simple blockquote
>> This is a nested blockquote
>>> Even deeper nesting

### 4. Code Blocks

```python
def hello_world():
    print("Hello, Markdown!")
    
class Example:
    def __init__(self):
        self.value = 42
```

```javascript
function calculateSum(a, b) {
    return a + b;
}
```

### 5. Tables

| Feature | Basic | Pro | Enterprise |
|---------|:------|:---:|----------:|
| Users | 10 | 100 | Unlimited |
| Storage | 5GB | 50GB | 500GB |
| Support | Email | 24/7 | Dedicated |
| Custom Domain | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Analytics | Basic | Advanced | Full Suite |

### 6. Images and Links

![Markdown Logo](https://markdown-here.com/img/icon256.png)
[Visit GitHub](https://github.com)

### 7. LaTeX Mathematical Expressions

Inline equation: $E = mc^2$

Block equation:
$$
\frac{-b \pm \sqrt{b^2 - 4ac}}{2a}
$$

$$
\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^2} = \frac{\pi^2}{6}
$$

### 8. Task Lists

- [x] Write the introduction
- [x] Add code examples
- [ ] Complete documentation
- [ ] Review and publish

### 9. Horizontal Rules

---
***
___

### 10. Advanced Table with Alignment

| Left-aligned | Center-aligned | Right-aligned |
|:------------|:-------------:|-------------:|
| col 3 is | some wordy text | $1600 |
| col 2 is | centered | $12 |
| zebra stripes | are neat | $1 |

### 11. Definition Lists

Term 1
: Definition 1

Term 2
: Definition 2a
: Definition 2b

### 12. Footnotes

Here's a sentence with a footnote[^1].

[^1]: This is the footnote content.

### 13. Custom HTML

<details>
<summary>Click to expand!</summary>

This is hidden content that can be expanded.
</details>

<div align="center">
  <h3>Centered content</h3>
  <p>This entire section is centered</p>
</div>

### 14. Emoji Support

:smile: :heart: :thumbsup: :rocket:

### 15. Mermaid Diagrams

```mermaid
graph TD;
    A-->B;
    A-->C;
    B-->D;
    C-->D;
```
```mermaid
flowchart TD;
    A["第1章 绪论"] --> B["第2章 相关概念与主要理论"];
    B --> C["第3章 影响因素分析"];
    C --> D["第4章 指标评价分析"];
    D --> E["第5章 问题与成因"];
    E --> F["第6章 主要对策"];
    F --> G["第7章 结论与展望"];
    
    subgraph Chapter1["第1章 绪论"]
        A1["1.1 研究背景"] --> A2["1.2 国内外研究现状"];
    end
    
    subgraph Chapter2["第2章 相关概念与主要理论"]
        B1["2.1 相关概念"] --> B2["2.2 主要理论"];
    end
    
    subgraph Chapter3["第3章 影响因素分析"]
        C1["3.1 案例概况"] --> C2["3.2 问卷调查"];
    end
    
    subgraph Chapter4["第4章 指标评价分析"]
        D1["4.1 指标体系"] --> D2["4.2 层次分析法"];
    end
    
    subgraph Chapter5["第5章 问题与成因"]
        E1["5.1 主要问题"] --> E2["5.2 资产端问题成因"];
    end
    
    subgraph Chapter6["第6章 主要对策"]
        F1["6.1 资产端优化策略"] --> F2["6.2 REITs模式创新"];
    end
    
    subgraph Chapter7["第7章 结论与展望"]
        G1["7.1 结论"] --> G2["7.2 展望"];
    end

```
### 16. Html Integration
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>欢迎页面</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .feature {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature p {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🌟 欢迎访问</h1>
        <p>这是一个精美的HTML页面示例，展示了现代网页设计的基本元素和样式。</p>
        
        <button class="btn" onclick="showAlert()">点击我</button>
        <button class="btn" onclick="changeColor()">改变颜色</button>
        
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>📱 响应式设计</h3>
                <p>适配各种设备屏幕</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>🎨 现代样式</h3>
                <p>美观的渐变和阴影</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>⚡ 交互功能</h3>
                <p>JavaScript增强体验</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showAlert() {
            alert('你好！欢迎使用这个页面！');
        }

        function changeColor() {
            const container = document.querySelector('.container');
            const colors = ['#ff6b6b', '#4ecdc4', '#45b7d1', '#96ceb4', '#feca57'];
            const randomColor = colors[Math.floor(Math.random() * colors.length)];
            container.style.borderLeft = `5px solid ${randomColor}`;
        }

        // 页面加载动画
        window.addEventListener('load', function() {
            const container = document.querySelector('.container');
            container.style.opacity = '0';
            container.style.transform = 'translateY(30px)';
            container.style.transition = 'all 0.6s ease';
            
            setTimeout(() => {
                container.style.opacity = '1';
                container.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
            }, 100);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

This comprehensive example showcases various Markdown features and formatting options. Note that some features might require specific Markdown processors or extensions to work properly.
